
'''紐西蘭政府''' ({{lang-mi|Te Kāwanatanga o Aotearoa}}) 是在[[新西兰|紐西蘭]]行使統治權的[[中央政府|中央政府]]。與大多數[[議會制|議會民主制]]一樣，「政府」一詞主要是指[[行政机关|行政部門]]。根據[[责任政府|問責政府]]的原則，紐西蘭政府在得到國會的支持下運作。<ref>Sir [[Kenneth_Keith|Kenneth Keith]], quoted in the [http://www.dpmc.govt.nz/cabinet/manual/intro.html Cabinet Manual] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/19991009163331/http://www.dpmc.govt.nz/cabinet/manual/intro.html|date=9 October 1999}}</ref>紐西蘭政府部長行使行政權力，並對[[紐西蘭眾議院|眾議院]]負責。內閣由多名高級部長組成（通常為20名），並由總理領導。[[新西兰总理|總理]]職位由能獲得眾議院多數議員的[[信任投票|信任票]]的人擔任。總理和其他部長由[[新西兰总督|紐西蘭總督]]（英女皇的代表）正式任命。按照慣例，總督會根據總理的建議任命部長。
== 術語 ==

[[紐西蘭議會建築群|國會建築群]]的行政大樓因其外型而通常被稱為「蜂巢」。大樓設有政府辦公室，亦是內閣開會的地方，因此「蜂巢」一詞有時會被轉喻指紐西蘭政府。紐西蘭政府的官方網站的網址亦為<code><nowiki>beehive.govt.nz</nowiki></code> 。 <ref>{{Cite web|title=About this website|url=https://www.beehive.govt.nz/about-this-site|access-date=18 August 2020|work=beehive.govt.nz|publisher=New Zealand Government|language=en-NZ|quote=Beehive.govt.nz is the official website of the New Zealand Government.}}</ref>

== 歷史 ==
[[File:The_Beehive_in_June_2012.jpg|左]]的[[蜂窩大廈|蜂巢大廈]]是[[中央政府所在地|紐西蘭政府所在地]]（行政部门）]]
1852年，在《紐西蘭憲法法》通過後，紐西蘭被英國授予自治權。紐西蘭的中央政府和當時六個省的政府隨後成立。在[[哈里·阿特金森（Harry_Atkinson）|哈里·阿特金森（Harry Atkinson）]]擔任總理期間，《1876年廢除省份法》廢除了這些省，使中央政府直接管轄全國。

1856年的塞維爾政府是第一任[[责任政府|問責政府]]，其對[[原住民|原住民]]政策以外的所有国内事务都有控制权。 <ref name="timeline">{{Cite web|title=Political and constitutional timeline|url=https://nzhistory.govt.nz/politics/milestones|access-date=1 May 2017|date=4 November 2016|publisher=Ministry for Culture and Heritage|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170408214941/https://nzhistory.govt.nz/politics/milestones|archive-date=8 April 2017}}</ref>在5月7日，[[亨利·休厄尔|亨利·塞維爾]]（Henry Sewell）被任命為「殖民地司」，被後世視為紐西蘭第一任總理。<ref>McIntyre, W. David. </ref> 直到1891年[[约翰·巴兰斯|約翰·巴倫斯]]（John Ballance）成立自由黨及建立自由黨政府之後，才出現了按照政黨派系成立的政府。紐西蘭總理自此同時是執政黨的領袖。<ref>McLean, Gavin (13 December 2016).</ref>





== 政府與皇室 ==
[[File:New_Zealand_Cabinet,_1981.jpg|缩略图]]
紐西蘭政府的正式稱號是女王陛下在紐西蘭的政府。 <ref>{{Cite web|title=Seal of New Zealand Act 1977|url=http://www.legislation.govt.nz/act/public/1977/0001/latest/whole.html?|access-date=30 April 2017|publisher=Parliamentary Counsel Office|language=en-NZ|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170817082155/http://www.legislation.govt.nz/act/public/1977/0001/latest/whole.html|archive-date=17 August 2017}}</ref>英女王[[伊丽莎白二世|伊利沙伯二世]]是紐西蘭國家元首。<ref name="constitution act">{{Cite web|title=Constitution Act 1986 No 114 (as at 17 May 2005), Public Act – New Zealand Legislation|url=http://www.legislation.govt.nz/act/public/1986/0114/latest/whole.html#dlm94204|access-date=7 December 2016|publisher=Parliamentary Counsel Office|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161223071437/http://www.legislation.govt.nz/act/public/1986/0114/latest/whole.html#dlm94204|archive-date=23 December 2016}}</ref>基於英國《1689年權利法案》，紐西蘭確立了國會至上的原則。然而，《紐西蘭憲法》仍然將将君主描述為「主權者」。

紐西蘭仍然保有許多皇家特權。例如 ，法律的制定需要得到御准 (Royal Assent)<ref>{{cite web|title=The Royal Assent|url=https://www.parliament.nz/en/get-involved/features-pre-2016/document/00NZPHomeNews031220091/the-royal-assent|access-date=30 April 2017|publisher=New Zealand Parliament|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171010094904/https://www.parliament.nz/en/get-involved/features-pre-2016/document/00NZPHomeNews031220091/the-royal-assent|archive-date=10 October 2017|url-status=live}}</ref>；英女王及其代表有權召集或解散國會以進行選舉<ref>{{cite web|title=The New Zealand Constitution|url=https://www.parliament.nz/resource/en-nz/00PLLawRP00011/502fa2135dd16543ca15974a028ad70161b80aba|access-date=30 April 2017|date=3 October 2005|publisher=New Zealand Parliament|pages=4–5|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170306212632/https://www.parliament.nz/resource/en-nz/00PLLawRP00011/502fa2135dd16543ca15974a028ad70161b80aba|archive-date=6 March 2017|url-status=live}}</ref>，談判和批准條約，簽署國際協議，及宣戰等。

英女王很少親自行使其行政權力。由於她通常 不居住在紐西蘭，因此她會任命一位[[新西兰总督|總督]]來代表她並行使她的大部分權力。<ref name="GG role">{{Cite web|title=The Role of the Governor-General|url=http://www.gg.govt.nz/role|access-date=30 April 2017|publisher=The Governor-General of New Zealand Te Kawana Tianara o Aotearoa|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170419033256/https://gg.govt.nz/role|archive-date=19 April 2017}}</ref>擔任此職位的人由[[新西兰总理|紐西蘭總理]]和其他部長選拔。總督沒有正式的任期限制。<ref>{{cite web|title=Letters Patent Constituting the Office of Governor-General of New Zealand|url=http://www.legislation.govt.nz/regulation/public/1983/0225/latest/whole.html|access-date=30 April 2017|publisher=Parliamentary Counsel Office}}</ref>

按照[[君主立宪制|君主立憲制]]的傳統規定，女王及其代表很少直接干預政治事務。<ref name="GG role">{{Cite web|title=The Role of the Governor-General|url=http://www.gg.govt.nz/role|access-date=30 April 2017|publisher=The Governor-General of New Zealand Te Kawana Tianara o Aotearoa|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170419033256/https://gg.govt.nz/role|archive-date=19 April 2017}}</ref> 君主對總督的選擇依從總理的建議，總督則根據部長的建議行使國家的行政權力。<ref name="constitution act">{{Cite web|title=Constitution Act 1986 No 114 (as at 17 May 2005), Public Act – New Zealand Legislation|url=http://www.legislation.govt.nz/act/public/1986/0114/latest/whole.html#dlm94204|access-date=7 December 2016|publisher=Parliamentary Counsel Office|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161223071437/http://www.legislation.govt.nz/act/public/1986/0114/latest/whole.html#dlm94204|archive-date=23 December 2016}}</ref>
== 議會中的政府 ==
[[File:20200508_New_Zealand_government_structure.svg|缩略图]]
根據[[西敏制|西敏制]]的慣例，[[责任政府|問責政府]]向[[新西兰议会|眾議院]]負責，而不是向君主。<ref name="system_of_government">{{Cite web|title=Our system of government|url=https://www.parliament.nz/en/visit-and-learn/how-parliament-works/our-system-of-government/|access-date=30 April 2017|publisher=New Zealand Parliament|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170308123708/https://www.parliament.nz/en/visit-and-learn/how-parliament-works/our-system-of-government/|archive-date=8 March 2017}}</ref> <ref name="glossary">{{Cite web|title=Glossary of Constitutional Terms|url=http://www.ourconstitution.org.nz/Glossary|access-date=1 May 2017|publisher=New Zealand Constitutional Advisory Panel|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170406042022/http://www.ourconstitution.org.nz/Glossary|archive-date=6 April 2017}}</ref>政府必須維持眾議院對其的支持和信任，以通過[[政府预算|政府預算]]及[[委任立法|主要立法]]。<ref>{{Cite book|last=Galligan|first=Brian|last2=Brenton|first2=Scott|title=Constitutional Conventions in Westminster Systems|date=2015|publisher=Cambridge University Press|isbn=9781107100244|pages=209|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=paQyCgAAQBAJ&pg=PA209|language=en}}</ref> <ref>{{Cite news|author=Bracewell-Worrall|first=Anna|title=What is confidence and supply… and how does it differ from a coalition?|url=https://www.newshub.co.nz/home/election/2017/10/what-is-confidence-and-supply-and-how-does-it-differ-from-a-coalition.html|accessdate=2 June 2018|work=[[Newshub|Newshub]]|date=4 October 2017|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180421235519/http://www.newshub.co.nz/home/election/2017/10/what-is-confidence-and-supply-and-how-does-it-differ-from-a-coalition.html|archivedate=21 April 2018}}</ref> 如果政府[[不信任动议|無法得到眾議院的信任]]，則必須辭職或舉行大選。 <ref>{{Cite book|last=Arwine|first=A.|last2=Mayer|first2=L.|title=The Changing Basis of Political Conflict in Advanced Western Democracies: The Politics of Identity in the United States, the Netherlands, and Belgium|date=2013|publisher=Springer|isbn=9781137306654|page=119|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=RCPVes3RmhUC&pg=PT119|language=en}}</ref>自1928年以來，沒有一屆政府在不信任動議投票中落敗，而因此不得不辭職。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Parties and Government|url=https://www.parliament.nz/en/visit-and-learn/how-parliament-works/parliamentary-practice-in-new-zealand/chapter-8-parties-and-government/|access-date=10 September 2019|work=www.parliament.nz|publisher=New Zealand Parliament|language=en}}</ref>
== 政府部長 ==
政府部長亦被稱為「王國政府部長」。他們負責制定和實施政策，以及向[[新西兰总督|紐西蘭總督]]提供建議。<ref name="ExecCouncil">{{Cite web|title=Executive Council|url=https://www.dpmc.govt.nz/cabinet/ministers/executive|access-date=30 April 2017|publisher=Department of the Prime Minister and Cabinet|language=en-NZ|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170514144936/http://dpmc.govt.nz/cabinet/ministers/executive|archive-date=14 May 2017}}</ref> 

=== 行政會議 ===
[[File:Appointment_of_the_New_Ministry_2020.jpg|缩略图]]

所有政府部長都是行政會議成員，他們大部分終身享有「[[尊敬的|尊敬的]]」的前綴，而總理則終身享有「非常尊敬的」的前綴。<ref>{{Cite web|title=The Honourable|url=https://www.dpmc.govt.nz/honours/overview/hon|access-date=30 April 2017|publisher=Department of the Prime Minister and Cabinet|language=en-NZ|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170408180932/http://www.dpmc.govt.nz/honours/overview/hon|archive-date=8 April 2017}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=The Right Honourable|url=https://www.dpmc.govt.nz/honours/overview/rthon|access-date=30 April 2017|publisher=Department of the Prime Minister and Cabinet|language=en-NZ|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170408180916/http://www.dpmc.govt.nz/honours/overview/rthon|archive-date=8 April 2017}}</ref>雖然總督不是行政會議成員，但他通常負責主持行政會議。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Executive Council – Cabinet Manual|url=https://cabinetmanual.cabinetoffice.govt.nz/1.18|access-date=30 April 2017|date=2008|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170407040923/https://cabinetmanual.cabinetoffice.govt.nz/1.18|archive-date=7 April 2017}}</ref>

=== 內閣 ===
內閣 ({{Lang-mi|Te Rūnanga}}) 是政府的高級決策機構。 <ref>{{Cite book|last=McLeay|first=Elizabeth|authorlink=Elizabeth McLeay|title=The Cabinet and Political Power in New Zealand|volume=5|date=1995|publisher=Oxford University Press|isbn=9780195583120|page=11}}</ref> <ref name="Cabinet1">{{Cite encyclopedia|accessdate=30 April 2017|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220070040/http://www.teara.govt.nz/en/cabinet-government/page-1|archivedate=20 December 2016}}</ref>總理負責主持內閣會議。<ref name="McLean2017">{{Cite encyclopedia|accessdate=30 April 2017|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170517231343/http://www.teara.govt.nz/en/premiers-and-prime-ministers|archivedate=17 May 2017}}</ref>總督會任命最有可能獲得眾議院信任以領導政府的人為總理。 <ref>{{Cite web|title=Cainet Manual 2008|url=http://cabinetmanual.cabinetoffice.govt.nz/2.2|access-date=21 September 2011|year=2008|work=cabinetmanual.cabinetoffice.govt.nz|publisher=[[Department_of_the_Prime_Minister_and_Cabinet_(New_Zealand)|Department of the Prime Minister and Cabinet]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080602101837/http://www.cabinetmanual.cabinetoffice.govt.nz/2.2|archive-date=2 June 2008}}</ref> 

總理然後建議總督任命其他部長。傳統上，所有內閣成員集體對內閣採取的行動負責，即所有內閣部長必須公開支持內閣的決定。<ref>{{Cite encyclopedia|accessdate=4 December 2020|language=en-NZ}}</ref>然而，自從在1993年引入[[联立制|聯立制]]（MMP）選舉制度以來<ref>{{Cite web|title=Electoral Act 1993 No 87 (as at 01 April 2020), Public Act – New Zealand Legislation|url=http://www.legislation.govt.nz/act/public/1993/0087/latest/whole.html|access-date=15 April 2020|publisher=Parliamentary Counsel Office}}</ref>，[[聯合政府|聯合政府]]內閣內的不同政黨可在某些問題上表達不一致的立場。<ref name="Eichbaum">{{Cite encyclopedia|accessdate=17 September 2018}}</ref>

國會的立法議程由內閣決定。 在每個新的議會任期開始時，總督會代表女王在國會[[御座致辞|發表講話]]，概述政府的政策和立法建議。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Speech from the Throne – Cabinet Manual|url=https://cabinetmanual.cabinetoffice.govt.nz/7.3|access-date=1 May 2017|date=2008|work=cabinetmanual.cabinetoffice.govt.nz|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170407041930/https://cabinetmanual.cabinetoffice.govt.nz/7.3|archive-date=7 April 2017}}</ref>
== 部門和其他公共部門組織 ==
紐西蘭的公共服務包括32個核心政府機構。它們由大約45,000名公務員組成<ref>{{Cite news|title=Civil servant numbers static|url=http://www.stuff.co.nz/national/politics/63817264/civil-servant-numbers-static|date=4 December 2014|accessdate=1 May 2017|work=Stuff.co.nz}}</ref>，為政府提供建議並向公眾提供服務。自1980年代以來，公共服務已經市場化。<ref>{{Cite encyclopedia|accessdate=9 November 2018}}</ref> 每個部門均由一名首席執行官領導，首席執行官會就該部門的表現向政府部長負責。反過來，部長對所管理的部門的行為承擔最終責任，並對眾議院負責。<ref name="Cabinet6">{{Cite encyclopedia|accessdate=30 April 2017|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170402212717/http://www.teara.govt.nz/en/cabinet-government/page-6|archivedate=2 April 2017}}</ref>

== 與地方政府的關係 ==
民選地方政府主要分為兩個層級，即[[紐西蘭一級行政區劃|區域議會 (Regional councils) 和區域當局 (Territorial authorities)。]]中央政府負責處理與紐西蘭全國及其國民有關的問題，而地方政府則負責「使社區能夠執行民主的內部決策和行動」，並「滿足當前和未來的對本地基礎設施、公共服務及監管職能的需求」。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Local Government Act 2002|url=http://www.legislation.govt.nz/act/public/2002/0084/latest/whole.html?search=sw_096be8ed8132e50b_50%2c000_25_se&p=1#DLM170873|access-date=9 November 2018|publisher=Parliamentary Counsel Office}}</ref>

== 現屆紐西蘭政府 ==

自2020年11月以來，現屆紐西蘭政府是[[新西兰工党|工黨]]政府，由總理[[傑辛達·阿德恩|賈辛達·阿登]]領導。[[多數派政府|多數派政府]]與[[奥特亚罗瓦新西兰绿党|綠黨]]有合作協議。<ref>{{Cite press release|accessdate=12 November 2020}}</ref>

